1. Install the sublime Text 2 
2. Install Package control manager
   How ?
  1 . ctrl+` this will open a small field below the editor
  2. Copy the python code from https://packagecontrol.io/installation#st2 link and paste it
  3. Close and open few times. Atleast 3 times. The package control manager will installed successfullly
3. Ctrl + shift + P and type "Install Package"
4. This will come with a new field. Type Coffeescript. That's it! 
